        "jsonBody": "={\n  \"messaging_product\": \"whatsapp\",\n  \"to\": \"{{ $('Member: Join Webhook').item.json.body.phone }}\",\n  \"type\": \"text\",\n  \"text\": { \"body\": \"Hey {{ $('Member: Join Webhook').item.json.body.name }}! Welcome to the AI for CAs community.\\n\\nYou'll get a daily morning drop — one AI tip for CA firms, straight to WhatsApp.\\n\\nIf you ever want to automate something specific in your firm, just message here and I'll look into it. — Saksham\" }\n}",
